<div class="content-panel centered standalone"></div>
<div class="feature-block">
<div class="content-panel left-column">
<div class="panel-heading">
<p>精品SPC<br /></p>
</div>
<div class="panel-body"><div class="list-pages-box">    <div class="list-pages-item">


<div class="feature-title">
<p><a href="/nicos-stupid-proposal">Uncle Nicolini的提案…大概吧。</a><br /></p>
</div>
<div class="feature-subtitle">
<p>译/搬运 <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sylvia-edith" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3779445); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3779445&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610159993" alt="Sylvia_Edith" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3779445)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sylvia-edith" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3779445); return false;">Sylvia_Edith</a></span><br /></p>
</div>
<br />
<em><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">在陆地上使用SPC-001的后果。应注意在鲨鱼尸体上书写的“搞错鱼了”带有讥讽和恐吓意味。&#32;&#32;&#32;项目编号：&#32;SPC-001&#32;鲨鱼殴打性能：&#32;SPC-001的使用显著提高了殴打鲨鱼行动的效率，并降低了对殴鲨人员造成的风险。SPC-001的有效射程远超已知的殴鲨手段，并被证实具有远超常规武器的威力。...</span></em></div>
    
    
    
    </div></div>
