<div class="spc-page-footer">
<p>作/译者（们） &#8212; <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dawntang" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5137332); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5137332&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610159995" alt="DawnTang" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5137332)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dawntang" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5137332); return false;">DawnTang</a></span></p>
</div>
</td>
